; Test commodity compare with recursive disparity
2024/01/01 Buy A
    Assets:Stocks    10 AAPL {$100.00}
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/02 Buy B
    Assets:Stocks    10 AAPL {200.00 EUR}
    Assets:Cash

test bal Assets:Stocks --lot-prices
      10 AAPL {$100}
    10 AAPL {EUR200}  Assets:Stocks
end test
